#: ../content/index.rst:11
msgid ""
"This package brings the functionality to automatically create a ticket with "
"configurable parameters to a freely chooseable point in time in relation to "
"an appointment."
msgstr ""

#: ../content/index.rst:13
msgid ""
"Ticket Creation is initiated in the AppointmentEdit mask under the section "
"'Ticket Creation'. A point in time relative to the appointment, as well as "
"ticket data can be configured. Recurring appointments are supported."
msgstr ""

